Text: "There was a country in the old fashion European continent full of sun, colors,\
  \ festivals and a marvelousness rich mix of culture, yes you have heard about him\
  \ hire and there lately, it might be a sign, is Portugal, what about this place;\
  \ well everything about it, rich and enchanting culture full of multiplicity, you\
  \ can see it with your eyes in the unique architecture, the diversity of people\
  \ and the festivities.\nDiversity and fun that\u2019s so much to see and experience\
  \ here, from the beaches to the hills, from the carnaval to the bar in the balcony.\
  \ Full of culture, past and people with so much to share.\nIf Experience Europa\
  \ in a less antique \u201Cclassic\u201D or uber sophisticated way is calling you\n\
  Portugal."
